  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They tried to educate the Belgians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that, that photograph that you have of me and my sister standing in front of a poster was an effort to educate the Belgians that the Jews really are dangerous and that they have a conspiracy of all of Europe and that you really should watch out for them.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you look at this picture carefully, you will see a V for resist-- for, for victory, which was already applied by the resistance, the Belgian resistance.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the Belgians didn't help them, not like in France, where the [INAUDIBLE] police themselves arrested the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So now the Germans imagined another kind of system where they, if they ask us to come, we had to come in and, and pick up a start at the high office of, of the German command.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I stood in line outside and got the star and had to give them my address.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And two weeks later, you got a convocation to come and report yourself to the trains for labor in Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And half the Jewish population, the immigrant Jewish population in, in Brussels by themselves went and reported to the trains.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Instead of going to, to work in Germany, of course, those trains went to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And only very few came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If you did not report to those trains, you now, of course, broke the law.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you, you couldn't live in your apartment anymore now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You went into hiding like Anne Frank.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And with the help of my, my school buddy whose father was a communist and the mother I had a wool shop-- she rented the premises next to her wool shop and was telling the landlord that she needed more space for her merchandise.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
